        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2679171336" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1970245695828517728">This book is something of an introduction to Anarcho-communism train of thought.<br/>However, I found almost all the arguments far too simplistic and without proper statistics or credibility to back them up, as usual with any suggestion anarchist society. <br/><br/>This book serves as a very good read to understand the train of thought that most anarchist subscribe to (At least of the anarcho-communist flavor), but fails in deeper analysis. I will continue to search for more answers in my quest of finding the </span>
  <span id="freeText1970245695828517728" style="display:none">This book is something of an introduction to Anarcho-communism train of thought.<br />However, I found almost all the arguments far too simplistic and without proper statistics or credibility to back them up, as usual with any suggestion anarchist society. <br /><br />This book serves as a very good read to understand the train of thought that most anarchist subscribe to (At least of the anarcho-communist flavor), but fails in deeper analysis. I will continue to search for more answers in my quest of finding the optimal societal options.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1970245695828517728" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
